{"name":"Kargoe, posessed","size":"medium","type":"Aire","tag":"lich","alignment":"LE","hitDice":"14","armorName":"chain mail","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":3,"otherArmorDesc":"17 (natural armor)","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":true,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"45 (+45)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"16","dexPoints":"10","conPoints":"14","intPoints":"20","wisPoints":"17","chaPoints":"20","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"13","customCr":"12 (8,400 XP)","customProf":4,"isLegendary":true,"legendariesDescription":"In this weakened state, the demilich only has 1 legendary action per round, which it _may_ use at the end of another creature's turn.","isLair":true,"lairDescription":"On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the demilich rolls a d20. On a result of 11 or higher, the demilich within [MON] takes a lair action to cause one of the following effects. It can't use the same effect two rounds in a row. Destroying the Astrolabe disables lair actions.","lairDescriptionEnd":"The ruined tower is warded against the magical travel of creatures the demilich hasn't authorized. Such creatures can't teleport into or out of the tomb's area or use planar travel to enter or leave it.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the archmage's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the archmage's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the archmage dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Legendary Resistance (3/day)","desc":"If [MON] fails a saving throw, he can choose to succeed instead."},{"name":"Abjurer's Ward (45)","desc":"[MON] has a pool of 45 temporary hit points. Whenever [MON] casts an abjuration spell, the ward regains twice the spell level in temp hp."},{"name":"Spell Resistance","desc":"[MON] has advantage on saving throws against spells and resistance against the damage of spells."},{"name":"Spellcasting","desc":"[MON] is posessed by a demilich which is still recovering it's magical abilities. It's spellcasting ability is Intelligence (spell save DC [INT SAVE], [INT ATK] to hit with spell attacks). It has the following spells readied\n\n> * Cantrips : _thorn whip, acid splash, shocking grasp, dancing lights, minor illusion, mage hand_\n> * (at will): _shield, wristpocket (permanent)_\n> * (2/day each): _counterspell, lightning bolt, banishment_\n> * (1/day each): _wall of force, mass suggestion, plane shift_"}],"actions":[{"name":"Glaive","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [STR ATK] to hit, reach 10 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [STR 1D10] slashing damage."},{"name":"Acid Splash","desc":"[MON] chooses one (or two adjacent) creature he can see within 60ft. Each target must save on DC [INT SAVE] dexterity or take [4d6] acid damage."},{"name":"Thorn Whip","desc":"_Melee Spell Attack:_ [CHA ATK] to hit, reach 30 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [4D6] piercing damage and the target is pulled 10ft closer to [MON]"},{"name":"Shocking Grasp","desc":"_Melee Spell Attack:_ [INT ATK] to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [4D8] lightning damage and the target can't use reactions until the start of its next turn."}],"bonusActions":[],"reactions":[{"name":"Counterspell","desc":"[MON] casts _counterspell_ (with a [INT ATK])."},{"name":"Shield","desc":"[MON] casts _shield_."},{"name":"Bitter Blood","desc":"When [MON] is hit with an attack it can choose to take [1d6] necrotic damage to spew blood over the attacker. On this and subsequent turns until the end of [MON]'s _next_ turn, the attacker takes [2d4] poison damage."}],"legendaries":[{"name":"Command Skinsplinter","desc":"The Skinsplinter shard within [MON] responds to the demilich's commands: _Melee Attack:_ [CHA ATK] to hit, range 20 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [3D6] piercing damage, [3d6] necrotic damage. Then [MON] heals for the damage dealt."}],"mythics":[],"lairs":[{"name":"Force of Personality","desc":"**Force of Personality**: Being in the same room as the demilich is taxing on the mind. All other creatures in the lair must a DC [CHA SAVE] wisdom saving throw or suffer a level of exhaustion."},{"name":"Cosmic Wind","desc":"**Cosmic Wind**: All ranged attacks within the lair have disadvantage until the next initiative count 20."},{"name":"Protective Resonance","desc":"**Protective Resonance:** [MON] regains [6d6] temporary hit points to his abjurer's ward."}],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"int","order":3},{"name":"cha","order":5}],"skills":[{"name":"arcana","stat":"int","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"deception","stat":"cha"},{"name":"history","stat":"int"},{"name":"intimidation","stat":"cha"},{"name":"religion","stat":"int"}],"damagetypes":[{"name":"cold","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"},{"name":"lightning","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"},{"name":"necrotic","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"},{"name":"poison","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"},{"name":"psychic","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"}],"specialdamage":[{"name":"spell damage","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"}],"conditions":[],"languages":[{"name":"Abyssal","speaks":true},{"name":"Aire","speaks":true},{"name":"Dwarvish","speaks":true},{"name":"Elvish","speaks":true},{"name":"Merling","speaks":true}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Kargoe","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":8,"damage":[]}